title: Ep. 175 - Cruel Monty - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
tags: ep  175  cruel monty  taarak mehta ka ooltah chashmah
shortDesc: Tapu's friend's cousin Monty visits Gokuldham Society. He is very rude and Tapu doesn't like him. Today Tapu and his friends are playing a cricket match, he is waiting to teach Monty a lesson.

title: Ep. 176 - The Bet - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: As Bhide gets hit by the ball while the children play cricket, an argument breaks out between Jethalal and Bhide. A cricket match is finalized between Bhide and Jhethalal on the following Saturday with the condition of the loser having to clean.

title: Ep. 177 - Gokuldham Premiere League - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: As the ladies and the children of the Gokuldham society decide to participate in the match as well, Tarak flips the coin for the team selection. Bhide and Jethalal, being the captains, choose their respective teams for the upcoming cricket match.

title: Ep. 178 - Jabardast Jetha VS Bindass Bhide  - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: When Babita declares to sponsor Jethalal's team, Mohan steps forward and sponsors Bhide's team. Both the teams get ready for the match and start practicing and making strategies in secret.

title: Ep. 179 - Getting Ready For The Match - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Both the team captains, Jethalal and Bhinde, give the pep talk to their respective teams and as they reach the compound to practice, an argument breaks out between the teams as to who practices first.

title: Ep. 180 - It's Showtime! - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: With Sundarlal's plan, Tapu Sena gathers a lot of sponsors for the match to bear the recurring expenses. Sundarlal and Monica host the match as the two teams perform song and dance before the match praising their respective teams.

title: Ep. 181 - Daya Makes Wonder - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The match begins with a boom as the 'Bindass Bhide' wins the toss and chooses to bat. Tapu plays brilliantly as expected by everyone but Daya shocks the whole team and the entire audience with her exceptional performance.

title: Ep. 182 - A Tight Competition - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: With a hattrick, Daya blows everyone's mind off just like Sonu does with her batting. Bhide's team stands at 84 runs where Jethalal's team requires 13 runs from 6 balls to win.

title: Ep. 183 - Mayhem In The Match - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: As the last run needs to be scored by Jethalal's Team to win the match, the police come and confiscate the bat and ball to stop the match stating that a night match without police permission is prohibited. What happens next? Stay Tuned!

title: Ep. 184 - The Breakfast Affair - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: A hungry Jethalal is unable to have his favorite breakfast as unexpected guests come over and finish the food off. However, he calms down and plans on romancing with Daya but Daya, on the other hand, decides to go to the mall.

title: Ep. 185 -  Jethalal Romances With Daya - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: While Daya is working in the kitchen, Jethalal comes and gets romantic with Daya. He starts whistling to tease her in a good way, but as usual, Daya cannot understand anything.
